{"tid":93233,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【三點九沈大師】大師：唔好太重倉 2017-1-24 15:45:10","createTime":"2017-01-24T09:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T04:15:59.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd358fb2fa8277be65506734f46b05a7dc3422b2","tid":93233,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T09:05:40.000Z","msg":"【三點九沈大師】大師：唔好太重倉<br />\n2017-1-24 15:45:10<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【三點九沈大師】大師：唔好太重倉 <br />\n<br />\n大市繼續反覆，上落幾十點，冇乜大方向，個別中細價股各自各精彩，國企就炒股改等因素上咗o黎。但係恒指反而停滯不前，重磅股比較力弱，暫時方向未清，今日唔好亂郁住喇，慎防返禮拜四結算，有機會挾一挾高結，呢一段只係觀望為主，唔好太重倉，亦無需要走晒啲貨，留返部份貨喺到睇住先，直至過完年之後先至有方向嘅。"},{"pid":"37bd3ce945ce08db5cb49edb83428ff199e72cf0","tid":93233,"uid":36482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T09:18:21.000Z","msg":"TRUMP講完野又等新年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新年後係咪等清明"},{"pid":"626b035572c85dce1a30411efcae7744d55932b6","tid":93233,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T09:51:40.000Z","msg":"減咗咁多日仲點重貨"},{"pid":"833b418ad82a0fc2067801255b6644aaa8082a01","tid":93233,"uid":65140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T09:58:34.000Z","msg":"橫掂都係9up<br />\n師父不如交代下你d 熊仔同put call輪好過啦<br />\n有娛樂性d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dece3f6fdf6af0b524d7037c7c5c5c15b133a61b","tid":93233,"uid":65140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T09:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/91231b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F91231b.jpg&h=c9f42e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/981125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F981125.jpg&h=af2464e5&s={SIZE